```

### 4. Error Handling

| Error Scenario | Handling |
|----------|----------|
| `model_id` not found in ApiSource | Fallback to first model + log::warn |
| `api_source_id` not found | Fallback to first ApiSource + first model |
| ApiSource has no models | `resolve_model()` returns `None`, agent spawn fails gracefully |
| Legacy config has `model_tier` but no `model_id` | Auto-migration on load via `assign_model_ids()` |
| Agent references deleted ApiSource | `resolve_model()` falls back to first ApiSource; UI shows "source not found" |

